The Blade will never die.
Subscribe to Technoblade: https://www.youtube.com/user/technothepig

Hit the bell next to the sub button to get notified when a new song is dropping and join my discord server for exclusive content! https://discord.gg/7tzRPEjzEX

Written by Derivakat & Derivakat Twitch Chat
